{"tid":2492531,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家係咪都唔記得咗8月份修改入境條例？！","createTime":"2021-04-17T07:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T07:47:32.000Z","uid":193220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7601bea6e2b9c772c9a86f9e42005bc5b4a4c7b9","tid":2492531,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/UAELIYBAQVGJ3O2NZWDYJFOLWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FUAELIYBAQVGJ3O2NZWDYJFOLWA%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=16160eaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FUAELIYBAQVGJ3O2NZWDYJFOLWA%2F&h=74021935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/UAELIYBAQVGJ3O2NZWDYJFOLWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n柒婆已經好撚癲<br />\n咩都做得出<br />\n八月份佢會玩機場大封鎖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會正審議《入境條例》修訂草案，包括容許保安局局長賦權予入境處處長等人，禁止某運輸工具運載特定人士，引公眾憂慮條文損港人出入境自由。在昨日由建制派主導的立法會法案委員會，沒有議員提出限制港人出入境自由問題，但立法會顧問有提出，港人入境自由受《基本法》保障，問修訂案是否「好大程度擴闊了（保安局局長）禁止人出入境的權力」。保安局副局長區志光則指，「好有信心」提出的修訂是符合《基本法》，聲言沒有擴闊相關權力。<br />\n<br />\n經過 3 次會議後，法案委員會主席葛珮帆已宣布完成審議，草案將提交至立法會大會。保安局表示，「如果一切順利」，「暫定希望（法例）2021 年 8 月 1 日生效」。"},{"pid":"5a16bf09173dd15b5275e845bd02ea567a6a2d7f","tid":2492531,"uid":93874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"柒婆已經唔介意俾人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柒婆:我冇得走 你地都冇得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f69c6ba85dc6609674e84f353ccb9655a8baade","tid":2492531,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"想禁止bno人士離港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}